{"tid":1325301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港示威者入選《時代雜誌》互聯網25大具影響力人物","createTime":"2019-07-16T23:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T00:17:13.000Z","uid":348,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f59e889b8224c173ebd6cdbf6500c96cbe03c2f1","tid":1325301,"uid":348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T23:51:19.000Z","msg":"美國《時代雜誌》公布互聯網25大具影響力人物，香港示威者榜上有名。《時代雜誌》說，在反修例示威活動中，無單一領導者，示威者使用網上討論區「連登」及通訊軟件「Telegram」決定行動，包括遊行至外國領事館，以及包圍警察總部。文章引述一位Telegram示威頻道的管理員形容，過程是「直接民主」。《時代雜誌》又說，網民在討論區令示威行動的帖文引起關注，Telegram的投票及聊天室功能，令示威者迅速動員或改變策略，而示威活動提示、法律援助資訊、諮詢及情緒支援，都是透過網上進行。 除了香港示威者，上榜的亦包括美國總統特朗普、哈里王子與夫人梅根等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05578c658213e6d99495a86a21b486e0d447d61e","tid":1325301,"uid":20291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:11:41.000Z","msg":"搞錯左，係香討呀"},{"pid":"9dbfe78a5cdc7e28215ea16f3e2b590d9010a2a5","tid":1325301,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:12:16.000Z","msg":"同侵並列"},{"pid":"bfe72e02f68804ce2f7566287e3013d58d414c30","tid":1325301,"uid":216417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05578c658213e6d99495a86a21b486e0d447d61e","tid":1325301,"uid":20291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:11:41.000Z","msg":"搞錯左，係香討呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:13:18.000Z","msg":"不割蓆﹐齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082fd7ad59b213f57b7be7cd6adb63942e866a5f","tid":1325301,"uid":266243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:16:18.000Z","msg":"香討 BK 呀 咩係連登"},{"pid":"f7cd2640b0f25689e206ef7ed3182169499ccc4a","tid":13253